item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - The Paradise Girl - Som2 2003 Project Album
item.description:
Hello!
I'm looking for this kpop album from 2003, from the Som2 project.
I only see it available on Bugs! but I can't register on that website T-T, does anyone have it to share, please?
Track list:
1 Intro
2 소녀시대 II
3 바래
4 함께해요 (Let's Get Together)
5 네멋대로해봐
6 I Turn To You
7 예지몽
8 Someday
9 바래 (Remix)
10 소녀시대 II (Instrumental)

Kisses...
